ygData.messageBody:
certain types of foods will last longer then other as well. like iron
rations. i find that milk doesnt last as long as water. but i do find that
elvin wine gives one hell of a buzz faster then the dwarvin brew. hang
overs seen to last longer with elvin wine too :) hope this helps

Danek Lonewolf
Lvl 50 druid Fennin ro
